"searching ``sys.path`` for the first entry ending in ``/lib``. You can "
"override the destination using ``target``, but note that this path must "
"be in ``sys.path`` to be able to subsequently import it.::"
msgstr ""
"``mip`` 将通过搜索 ``sys.path`` 来检测文件系统上的适当位置，查找以 ``/lib`` 结尾的第一个条目。您可以使用 "
"``target`` 覆盖目标，但请注意，此路径必须在 ``sys.path`` 中才能随后导入。::"

