msgstr ":term:`mpremote` 还可以从主机本地文件系统中存储的文件安装软件包::"

#: ../../reference/packages.rst:106
msgid ""
"This is especially useful for testing packages during development and for"
" installing packages from local clones of GitHub repositories. Note that "
"URLs in ``package.json`` files must use forward slashes (\"/\") as "
"directory separators, even on Windows, so that they are compatible with "
"installing from the web."
msgstr ""
"这对于在开发期间测试软件包以及从 GitHub 仓库的本地克隆安装软件包特别有用。"
"请注意，``package.json`` 文件中的 URL 必须使用正斜杠（\"/\"）作为目录分隔符，"
"即使在 Windows 上也是如此，以便与从 Web 安装兼容。"

#: ../../reference/packages.rst:112
msgid "Installing packages manually"
msgstr "手动安装软件包"

#: ../../reference/packages.rst:114
msgid ""
"Packages can also be installed (in either .py or .mpy form) by manually "
"copying the files to the device. Depending on the board this might be via"
" USB Mass Storage, the :term:`mpremote` tool (e.g. ``mpremote fs cp "
"path/to/package.py :package.py``), :term:`webrepl`, etc."
msgstr ""
"软件包也可以通过手动将文件复制到设备中来安装(以.py或.mpy形式)。根据主板的不同，这可能是通过USB大容量存储， "
":term:`mpremote` 工具(例如 :``mpremote fs cp path/to/package.py:package.py`` "
")， :term:`webrepl` 等。"

#: ../../reference/packages.rst:120
msgid "Writing & publishing packages"
msgstr "编写和发布软件包"

#: ../../reference/packages.rst:122
msgid ""
"Publishing to :term:`micropython-lib` is the easiest way to make your "
"package broadly accessible to MicroPython users, and automatically "
"available via ``mip`` and ``mpremote`` and compiled to bytecode. See "
"https://github.com/micropython/micropython-lib for more information."
msgstr ""
"发布到 :term:`micropython-lib` 是让MicroPython用户广泛访问您的包的最简单方法，并且可以通过 ``mip`` 和"
" ``mpremote`` 自动获得并编译为字节码。更多信息请参见https://github.com/micropython"
"/micropython-lib。"

#: ../../reference/packages.rst:127
msgid ""
"To write a \"self-hosted\" package that can be downloaded by ``mip`` or "
"``mpremote``, you need a static webserver (or GitHub) to host either a "
"single .py file, or a ``package.json`` file alongside your .py files."
msgstr ""
"要编写可以通过 ``mip`` 或 ``mpremote`` "
"下载的“自托管”包，您需要一个静态web服务器(或GitHub)来托管单个.py文件或与.py文件一起的 ``package.json`` 文件。"

